[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "Thence, notwithstanding all they had endured, they proceeded to Bagdad.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "Alas! it is I that have made you wretched! why did you not let me perish miserably, rather than afford me your generous relief?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000005_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000005_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "What melancholy return have you received for your care and respect?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "\"Fetnah,\" said the caliph, without bidding her rise, \"I think you charge me with violence and injustice.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000008_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000008_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "Speak freely, you know the natural goodness of my disposition, and that I love to do justice.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "The caliph was not displeased with Fetnah for the freedom of these words; \"But may I,\" said he, \"rely on the assurance you give me of Ganem's virtue?\" \"Yes,\" replied Fetnah, \"you may.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "I went further yet: you know the tyranny of love: I felt some tender inclination rising in my breast.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000010_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000010_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "He perceived it; but far from availing himself of my frailty, and notwithstanding the flame which consumed him, he still remained steady in his duty, and all that his passion could force from him were the words I have already repeated to your majesty, That which belongs to the master is forbidden to the slave.'\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "Was there any need of staying a whole month after my return, before you sent me word where you were?\" \"Commander of the true believers,\" answered Fetnah, \"Ganem went abroad so very seldom, that you need not wonder we were not the first that heard of your return.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "Fetnah concluded, that he had not been able to survive the pain of losing her.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "She spend the whole day and the thousand pieces of gold in giving alms at the mosques, and returned to the palace in the evening.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000016_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000016_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "Through all the rags that covered them, notwithstanding the impression the sun has made on their faces, I discovered a noble air, not to be commonly found in those people I relieve.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000016_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000016_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "I carried them both to my house, and delivered them to my wife, who was of the same opinion with me. She caused her slaves to provide them good beds, whilst she herself led them to our warm bath, and gave them clean linen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "The caliph's favourite having dried up hers, said to Ganem's mother, \"Be so kind as to tell us your misfortunes, and recount your story.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000020_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000020_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "You are no longer his enemies.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "Fetnah would have proceeded, but the syndic of the jewellers coming in interrupted her: \"Madam,\" said he to her, \"I come from seeing a very moving object, it is a young man, whom a camel driver had just carried to an hospital: he was bound with cords on a camel, because he had not strength enough to sit.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000024_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000024_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "Ganem,\" added she, \"it is not you that I address!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000024_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000024_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "The son of Abou Ayoub, however indisposed, would know the voice of Fetnah.\" At the name of Fetnah, Ganem (for it was really he) opened his eyes, sprang up, and knowing the caliph's favourite; \"Ah! madam,\" said he, \"by what miracle\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000024_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000024_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "He could say no more; such a sudden transport of joy seized him that he fainted away. Fetnah and the syndic did all they could to bring him to himself; but as soon as they perceived he began to revive, the syndic desired the lady to withdraw, lest the sight of her should heighten his disorder.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "The young man having recovered, looked all around, and not seeing what he sought, exclaimed, \"What is become of you, charming Fetnah?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "Fetnah then said, \"Let us bless Heaven for having brought us all together.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000026_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000026_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "This said, she embraced the mother and the daughter, and went away.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "Matters being so ordered, the syndic announced Fetnah's coming to the sick man, who was so transported to see her, that he was again near fainting away, \"Well, Ganem,\" said she, drawing near to his bed, \"you have again found your Fetnah, whom you thought you had lost for ever.\" \"Ah! madam,\" exclaimed he, eagerly interrupting her, \"what miracle has restored you to my sight?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "I thought you were in the caliph's palace; he has doubtless listened to you.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000030_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000030_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "You have dispelled his jealousy, and he has restored you to his favour.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "\"Yes, my dear Ganem,\" answered Fetnah, \"I have cleared myself before the commander of the true believers, who, to make amends for the wrong he has done you, bestows me on you for a wife.\" These last words occasioned such an excess of joy in Ganem, that he knew not for a while how to express himself, otherwise than by that passionate silence so well known to lovers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000032_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000032_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "They were at the door waiting for that moment.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000032_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000032_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "Ganem's face was bathed with them, as well as his mother's and sisters; and Fetnah let fall abundance.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "He told them, that having taken refuge in a small village, he there fell sick; that some charitable peasants had taken care of him, but finding he did not recover, a camel driver had undertaken to carry him to the hospital at Bagdad.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000033_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000033_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "Fetnah also told them all the uneasiness of her imprisonment, how the caliph, having heard her talk in the tower, had sent for her into his closet, and how she had cleared herself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "This said, she went to the palace, and soon returned with a purse containing a thousand pieces of gold, which she delivered to the syndic, desiring him to buy apparel for the mother and daughter. The syndic, who was a man of a good taste, chose such as were very handsome, and had them made up with all expedition.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "The mother and daughter were mounted on mules belonging to the palace, and whilst Fetnah on another mule led them by a bye way to the prince's court, Jaaffier conducted Ganem, and brought him into the hall of audience.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000036_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000036_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "The caliph was highly pleased with Ganem's reply, and assigned him a considerable pension.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000036_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000036_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "He then descended from his throne, and causing only Ganem and the grand vizier, follow him, retired into his own apartment.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1594_135914_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1594/135914/1594_135914_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1594",
        "content": "Not questioning but that Fetnah was in waiting, with Abou Ayoub's widow and daughter, he caused them to be called in.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
